snippet.title: Technobabylon character teaser: Latha Sesame
snippet.description:
Available on Steam and GOG, coming to iPhone/iPad on August 16, 2017

Other character teasers:
Charlie Regis: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w6Z5-KHbKXQ
Max Lao: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6nt6cO4YqRk

Latha Sesame from the upcoming Technobabylon: a cyberpunk adventure game coming this spring from Wadjet Eye Games!
http://www.technobabylon-game.com

Latha Sesame, a jobless agoraphobe addicted to the Trance, has become targeted for assassination. Without knowing who to trust, she must face the dangers of “meatspace” and survive a fate that has invisibly ruled her entire life.


Technobabylon developed by: Technocrat Games
Published by: Wadjet Eye Games
Latha Sesame voiced by: Crystal Lonnquist (http://www.crystal-lonnquist.com/)
Art by: Ben Chandler
Music by: Premium Beats

Follow the development on Twitter with @wadjeteyegames and @technocratgames!

http://www.wadjeteyegames.com
http://www.technocratgames.com
